title: Stunning 1 Bedroom Unit Fully Renovated!
posting_body: ['FOUNTAIN PLAZA IN SAN JOSE RADIATES STYLE AND SOPHISTICATION', 'From the inside out – right in the center of Silicon Valley.', 'Vibrant decor and Spanish-influenced design lend a traditional vibe, while tech-savvy details and beautiful landscaping keeps things modern and always relaxed.', 'Work, connect, play and get inspired at Fountain Plaza.', '**Greystar California, Inc., Broker License #01525765**Please consult the community leasing office to determine applicable licensed company.', 'Call Now:', 'Need more information?', 'Copy this link:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 634 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Personal Balconies*', '- Maple, Raised-Panel Kitchen Cabinets', '- Loft-Style Floor Plans*', '- Wired for Alarm System', '- Spiral Staircases*', '- Elevator*', '- Kitchen Islands*', '- Built-In Desks*', '- Full-Size Washers and Dryers', '- Garden-Style Soaking Tubs*', '- Oversized Closets*', '- Wired for Ceiling Fans in Bedrooms and Living Room*', 'Community Amenities', '- 24/7 Complete Fitness Center', '- Relaxing Spa', '- Business Center', '- Additional Storage Available', '- Garage or Covered Parking*', '- Gated Community', '- Furnished Units Available*', '- See Sales Associate for Details.', '- Resort-Style Pool', '- Close to Hiking and Biking Trails', '- Minutes from Downtown San Jose', '- Close to Shopping and Fine Dining', '- We Love Pets!*', '- Resident Clubhouse', '- Easy Access to Highways 87, 280, 101 and 880', '- Conference Room', '- Near Public Transportation', '*Restrictions Apply.', 'Income Requirements:', '3x the amount of rent', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Sunday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Fountain Plaza (CA)', '190 ryland Street, San Jose, CA, 95110', 'XlTkq18Qj']
